      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Homelab Uptime Monitor\n\n**Schedule:** Every 5 minutes\n**Alert channel:** Slack\n\n### Branch 1 — HTTP Checks (top)\nCheck → if DOWN → wait 10s → recheck → if still DOWN → :red_circle: alert + link\nThreshold: statusCode < 500 (401/403 = UP)\n**33 sites:** 27 homelab + 6 external (Gemini, Google Workspace, CrowdStrike, HiBob, Let's Encrypt, Okta)\n\n### Branch 2 — Status Page APIs (bottom)\nFetch public status APIs → parse indicator → if not `none` → :warning: alert + status page link\n**9 services:** Claude, OpenAI, GitHub, Cloudflare, Slack, Atlassian, Zoom, JumpCloud, Monday",
        "height": 340,
        "width": 520,
        "color": 4
      },
